item.title: [HIVE-21619] Print timestamp type without precision in SQL explain extended
item.description: Hive dialect should print timestamp type without precision in generated SQL, since currently Hive does not support user-defined precision.
item.summary: Print timestamp type without precision in SQL explain extended

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
